<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="on-behalf-of-sb-on-sbs-behalf">on behalf of sb / on sb's behalf</h1>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>代表：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I, on behalf of our class, welcome you warmly and sincerely.
我代表我们班级，真诚、热情地欢迎你。</p><footer>2014 天津书面表达</footer></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>为了某人；因为某人：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They write letters of recommendation on behalf of students.
他们为学生写推荐信。</p><footer>北师大⑧ – 23</footer></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Don’t worry on my behalf.
别为我担心。</p></div></div>